* adds the content type to the transcation name "node_page_view.CONTENTTYPE" and custom paramenter "node.type/node.nid".
* adds user.uid and user.name to newrelic transcations for better debugging.
* adds custom parameter "node.og" indicates if the current node belongs to og group or not.
* mark the current transcations as background if the uid = 1 (admin), so it would not affect on performance rank.